BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:GenericCalendarEvent_2193213
DTSTAMP:20260307T172708Z
CREATED:20251229T183227Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T181013Z
SEQUENCE:1772043013
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260403T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260403T193000
SUMMARY:MO Girls 2017/2018 West Ham - CHAMPIONS CUP
DESCRIPTION:CHAMPIONS CUP<br>FRIDAY - 4/3/2026<br><br>SLSG Champions Cup:
 <br>The Champions Cup is a celebration event of our Living Legacy
  Foundation\, which helps provide scholarships for players in financial
  need.  We will also be collecting used soccer gear.  Coaches and team
  leaders are encouraged to help substitute\, but let the players coach
  themselves on the field\, and let the game be the teacher. Players are
  encouraged to RESPECT all aspects of the game.<br><br>SLSG SOCCER CLUB
  MISSION STATEMENT:<br>To build the Best Club in the Country\, a Club that
  positively impacts the development of our players on and off the field
  and our community.<br><br>DETAILS:<br>• 5v5 - U6 to U12 - Friday 4/3 -
  10 AM to 7:30 PM.<br>• Each team gets two 50-minute games\, consisting
  of two twenty-five-minute halves. If the tournament runs on time\, you
  should get 5 minutes to warm up. Some teams will receive a bonus (3rd)
  crossover game to help balance the odd-numbered brackets. We try to
  schedule brackets in a four-hour window.<br>• All weather-related issue
  updates will be posted on http://twitter.com/SLSGfacilities.<br>• There
  are no official bracket winners or prizes. This is a celebration event
  for our Living Legacy Program. <br>• No Refs. Team Leaders and players
  work together in unity to manage the game.<br>• 5v5 games (4 plus a
  goalie).<br>• The home team wears white. The away team wears all dark.
  Home and away are listed on the schedule.<br>• Kick-ins - no throw-ins
 <br>• If your game starts late\, then you will be shorted. Please be
  respectful to your opponent by showing up early and being ready to play
  when the clock starts.<br><br>DATES:<br>• Double Check Schedule 3/12\,
  3/19\, 3/28\, 4/2<br>• Gameday 4/3<br><br>RULES:<br>NO REFS - PLAYERS
  AND TEAM LEADERS MANAGE THE GAME - FIFA RULES APPLY EXCEPT:<br>• 5v5
  games (4 plus a goalie)<br>• Pass-ins instead of throw-ins<br><br>
 LIVING LEGACY FOUNDATION:<br>The SLSG Living Legacy Fund is an endowment
  that allows for scholarships to be awarded to deserving players who have
  talent and passion but may not have the financial resources to join the
  club. Scholarships are awarded by an endowment board made up of
  individuals inside and outside the club\, who weigh criteria including
  financial need\, character\, and passion for the game.<br><br>Donation
  link:<br>&#34\;https://secure.qgiv.com/for/slsgf/&#34\;<br><br>UPPER 90
  SHOE COLLECTION:<br>Used soccer shoes\, uniforms\, jerseys\, shorts\,
  socks\, training shirts\, and ball collection will be donated to support
  teams in Zambia\, Uganda\, Honduras\, Haiti\, and locally in St. Louis.
  We will have drop-off bins on the North Patio between fields 1\, 2\, and
  3.<br><br>ATTENDANCE EXPECTATIONS:<br>All players are to update their
  attendance on Playmetrics. All SLSG teams from U6 to U12 are
  automatically in the Champions Cup with no registration needed.  All
  games will be played. If you need players\, fill out the Team Leaders
  &amp\; Need Players form and tell us how many you need and we will find
  you players.  We have many players looking to play. <br>
 https://bit.ly/ChampionsCup-teamleader-needplayers-form<br><br>If you are
  playing a team that&#39\;s short on players\, please give them your subs
  so everyone plays and it&#39\;s still 5v5. If there still aren&#39\;t
  enough players\, please shorten the field and play 4v4\, or even 3v3\,
  depending on the number of players.<br><br>WANTING TO GUEST PLAY ON A 2ND
  TEAM?<br>If you are interested in guest playing for a 2nd team in the
  event\, please fill out this form\, and we will see if we can match you
  up with a team needing a player.<br>
 https://bit.ly/CHAMPIONScup-IwantTOguest<br><br>CHAMPIONS CUP - 2026 -
  GENERAL INFORMATION<br>https://bit.ly/SLSG-ONEday-Generalinfo
LOCATION:1 Soccer Park Rd\, Fenton\, MO 63026\, USA
STATUS:CONFIRMED
URL:https://playmetrics.com
END:VEVENT
